snippet.title: Super Yoshi / Yoshi's Egg DS Remake (UNRELEASED 2007)
snippet.description: This is a remake of Yoshi's Egg developed by GameFreak in 2007, built in what would become Pokemon Black and White's engine. Found in the BW source code leak as part of the Sparceleak.
